N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 22.12 - Plant

State Regulations

Plant means the land, buildings, surroundings, facilities, and equipment, whether owned or operated by one or more persons, constituting a single operating unit or establishment for the receiving, or
handling, or processing of milk or milk products as determined by the
commissioner. Notes
